| Redshift | $M_{cut}=10^4 M_\odot$ | $M_{cut}=10^5 M_\odot$ | $M_{cut}=5\times 10^5 M_\odot$ | $M_{cut}=10^6 M_\odot$ |
|----------|------------------------|------------------------|--------------------------------|------------------------|
| 7.0      | 0.0443                 | 0.1821                 | 0.2903                         | 0.3359                 |
